"<emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-tab\">zavihkov</link></"
"emphasis>"

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Widgets"
msgstr "Gradniki"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:320 ui.docbook:1348 ui.docbook:1401 ui.docbook:1490
#: ui.docbook:1567 ui.docbook:1627 ui.docbook:1725 ui.docbook:1758
#: ui.docbook:1846 ui.docbook:1946
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Central Widget"
msgstr "Osrednji gradniki"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main area of the running application. This might be the document you are "
"editing in a word processor or the board of a game like Chess."
msgstr ""
"Glavno področje delujoče aplikacije. To je lahko dokument, ki ga urejate v "
"urejevalniku besedil, ali igralna plošča igre, kot je šah."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "Button"
msgstr "Gumb"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "These can be clicked with the &LMB; to perform an action."
msgstr "Te lahko kliknete z &LMB;, da izvedete dejanje."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Breadcrumb"
msgstr "Drobtina (Breadcrumb)"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the path in a hierarchical system, such as a filesystem. Click on any "
"part of the path to go up in the tree to that location. Click on the arrow "
"to the right of part of the path to go to another child element of that path."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje pot v hierarhičnem sistemu, kot je datotečni sistem. Kliknite "
"katerikoli del poti, da se po drevesu povzpnete do te lokacije. Kliknite "
"puščico desno od dela poti, da se premaknete na drug podrejeni element te "
"poti."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check Box"
msgstr "Potrditveno polje"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These can be clicked to select and unselect items. They are typically used "
"in a list of several selections. Selected items typically display a check "
"mark, whereas unselected items will have an empty box."
msgstr ""
"Potrditvena polja lahko kliknete, da izberete in prekličete izbiro "
"elementov. Običajno se uporabljajo na seznamu z večimi izbirami. Izbrani "
"elementi običajno prikazujejo kljukico, neizbrani elementi pa imajo prazno "
"polje."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Selector"
msgstr "Izbirnik barve"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows a color to be selected for various purposes, such as changing "
"the color of text. For more information, see <xref linkend=\"colors\"/>"
msgstr ""
"To omogoča izbiro barve za različne namene, kot je spreminjanje barve "
"besedila. Za več informacij glejte <xref linkend=\"colors\"/>"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "Combo Box"
msgstr "Kombinirano polje"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A combination of a <link linkend=\"visualdict-drop-down-box\">Drop Down Box</"
"link> and a <link linkend=\"visualdict-text-box\">Text Box</link>. You can "
"select an option from the list, or type in the text box. Some combo boxes "
"may automatically complete entries for you, or open the list with a list of "
"choices that match what you have typed."
msgstr ""
"Kombinacija <link linkend=\"visualdict-drop-down-box\">spustnega polja</"
"link> in <link linkend=\"visualdict-text-box\">besedilnega polja</link>. "
"Izberete lahko možnost s seznama ali vnesete v besedilno polje. Nekatera "
"kombinirana polja lahko samodejno dokončajo vnose namesto vas ali odprejo "
"seznam s seznamom možnosti, ki se ujemajo s tem, kar ste vnesli."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context Menu"
msgstr "Kontekstni meni"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many user interface elements in the &plasma; Workspace and in Applications "
"contain a context menu, which can be opened by clicking on something with "
"the &RMB;. This menu contains options and actions that usually affect the "
"user interface element that was right-clicked."
msgstr ""
"Veliko elementov uporabniškega vmesnika v &plasma; delovnem prostoru in v "
"aplikacijah vsebuje kontekstni meni, ki ga lahko odprete s klikom na nekaj z "
"&RMB;. Ta meni vsebuje možnosti in dejanja, ki običajno vplivajo na element "
"uporabniškega vmesnika, ki je bil kliknjen z desno tipko miške."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dialog Box"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A small window that appears above a larger application window. It may "
"contain a message, warning, or configuration panel, among others."
msgstr ""
"Majhno okno, ki se prikaže nad večjim oknom aplikacije. Med drugim lahko "
"vsebuje sporočilo, opozorilo ali konfiguracijsko ploščo."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drop Down Box"
msgstr "Spustno polje"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "This provides a list of items, from which you may select one."
msgstr "To ponuja seznam elementov, s katerega lahko izberete enega."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon"
msgstr "Ikona"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A graphical representation of something, such as a file or action. They "
"typically, but not always, also contain a text description, either beneath "
"or to the right of the icon."
msgstr ""
"Grafična predstavitev nečesa, na primer datoteke ali dejanja. Običajno, "
"vendar ne vedno, vsebujejo tudi besedilni opis pod ikono ali desno od nje."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon List"
msgstr "Seznam ikon"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This provides a list of items represented by an <link linkend=\"visualdict-"
"icon\">Icon</link> and a description. It is typically used in the left panel "
"of configuration panels to allow selection from various types of "
"configuration categories."
msgstr ""
"To zagotavlja seznam elementov, predstavljenih z <link linkend=\"visualdict-"
"icon\">ikono</link> in opisom. Običajno se uporablja na levi plošči "
"konfiguracijskih plošč, da omogoči izbiro iz različnih vrst kategorij "
"konfiguracije."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "List Box"
msgstr "Polje s seznamom"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a list of items that typically allows multiple items to be selected. "
"To select a group of contiguous items, press the &Shift; key and click the "
"first and last items. To select multiple items that are not contiguous, "
"press the &Ctrl; key and select the desired items."
msgstr ""
"To je seznam elementov, ki običajno omogoča izbiro več elementov. Če želite "
"izbrati skupino sosednjih elementov, pritisnite &Shift; in kliknite prvi in "
"zadnji element. Če želite izbrati več elementov, ki niso sosednji, "
"pritisnite &Ctrl; in izberite želene elemente."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu"
msgstr "Meni"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A list of selections, that usually perform an action, set an option, or "
"opens a window. These can be opened from <link linkend=\"visualdict-menubar"
"\">menubars</link> or <link linkend=\"visualdict-menu-button\">menu buttons</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Seznam izbir, ki običajno izvedejo dejanje, nastavijo možnost ali odprejo "
"okno. Te je mogoče odpreti iz <link linkend=\"visualdict-menubar\">menijskih "
"vrstic</link> ali <link linkend=\"visualdict-menu-button\">menijskih gumbov</"
"link>."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menubar"
msgstr "Menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are located at the top of nearly every window and provide access to "
"all the functions of the running application. For more information, see "
"<xref linkend=\"menus\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Nahajajo se na vrhu skoraj vsakega okna in omogočajo dostop do vseh funkcij "
"delujoče aplikacije. Za več informacij glejte <xref linkend=\"menus\"/>."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Button"
msgstr "Menijski gumb"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A special type of <link linkend=\"visualdict-button\">button</link> that "
"opens a <link linkend=\"visualdict-menu\">menu</link>."
msgstr ""
"Posebna vrsta <link linkend=\"visualdict-button\">gumba</link>, ki odpre "
"<link linkend=\"visualdict-menu\">meni</link>."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panel <emphasis>or</emphasis> Sidebar <emphasis>or</emphasis> Tool View"
msgstr ""
"Plošča <emphasis>ali</emphasis> Stranska vrstica <emphasis>ali</emphasis> "
"Pogled orodja"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are located on the sides or bottom of the <link linkend=\"visualdict-"
"central-widget\">central widget</link> and allow you to perform many "
"different tasks in an application. A text editor might provide a list of "
"open documents in one, while a word processor might allow you to select a "
"clip art image."
msgstr ""
"Nahajajo se ob straneh ali na dnu <link linkend=\"visualdict-central-widget"
"\">osrednjega pripomočka</link> in vam omogočajo izvajanje številnih "
"različnih nalog v aplikaciji. Urejevalnik besedil lahko v njem ponudi seznam "
"odprtih dokumentov, urejevalnik besedil pa vam lahko omogoči izbiro slike "
"izrezka."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid "Progress Bar"
msgstr "Vrstica napredka"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A small bar that indicates that a long-running operation is being performed. "
"The bar may indicate how much of the operation has completed, or it may "
"simply bounce back and forth to indicate that the operation is in progress."
msgstr ""
"Majhna vrstica, ki označuje, da se izvaja dolgotrajna operacija. Vrstica "
"lahko označuje, koliko operacije je bila končana, ali pa preprosto poskakuje "
"naprej in nazaj, kar pomeni, da je operacija v teku."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Radio Button"
msgstr "Izbirni gumb"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are used in a list of options, and only permit one of the options in "
"the list to be selected."
msgstr ""
"Uporabljajo se na seznamu možnosti in dovoljujejo izbiro samo ene od "
"možnosti na seznamu."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrollbar"
msgstr "Drsni trak"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to navigate a document."
msgstr "Omogoča krmarjenje po dokumentu."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slider"
msgstr "Drsnik"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows a numeric value to be selected by moving a small bar either "
"horizontally or vertically across a line."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro številske vrednosti s premikanjem majhne vrstice vodoravno "
"ali navpično čez črto."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spin Box"
msgstr "Vrtilno polje"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This permits a numerical value to be selected, either by using the up and "
"down arrows to the right of the box to raise or lower the value, "
"respectively, or by typing the value into the <link linkend=\"visualdict-"
"text-box\">text box</link>."
msgstr ""
"To omogoča izbiro številske vrednosti, bodisi z uporabo puščic gor in dol na "
"desni strani polja za zvišanje ali znižanje vrednosti, bodisi z vnosom "
"vrednosti v <link linkend=\"visualdict-text-box\" >besedilno polje</link>."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status Bar"
msgstr "Statusna vrstica"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are located at the bottom of many applications and display information "
"about what the application is currently doing. For instance, a web browser "
"might indicate the progress of loading a web page, while a word processor "
"might display the current word count."
msgstr ""
"Ti se nahajajo na dnu številnih aplikacij in prikazujejo informacije o tem, "
"kaj aplikacija trenutno počne. Spletni brskalnik lahko na primer prikazuje "
"potek nalaganja spletne strani, urejevalnik besedil pa lahko prikaže "
"trenutno število besed."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>Tab</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>Zavihek</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These appear at the top of an area of a window, and permit that area of the "
"window to be changed to a variety of different selections."
msgstr ""
"Prikažejo se na vrhu območja okna in omogočajo, da se to območje okna "
"spremeni v vrsto različnih izbir."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Area"
msgstr "Območje besedila"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows a large amount of text to be typed in, typically multiple lines or "
"paragraphs. Unlike a <link linkend=\"visualdict-text-box\">Text Box</link>, "
"pressing &Enter; will usually result in a line break."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vnos velike količine besedila, običajno več vrstic ali odstavkov. Za "
"razliko od <link linkend=\"visualdict-text-box\">besedilnega polja</link>, "
"pritisk &Enter; običajno povzroči prelom vrstice."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Box"
msgstr "Besedilno polje"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A single-line text entry that allows a small amount of text to be typed in. "
"Typically, pressing &Enter; will perform the same action as clicking the "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Enovrstični vnos besedila, ki omogoča vnos majhne količine besedila. "
"Običajno bo pritisk na &Enter; izvedel isto dejanje kot klik na gumb "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Titlebar"
msgstr "Naslovna vrstica"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is located at the top of every window. It contains the name of the "
"application and usually information about what the application is doing, "
"like the title of the web page being viewed in a web browser or the filename "
"of a document open in a word processor."
msgstr ""
"To se nahaja na vrhu vsakega okna. Vsebuje ime aplikacije in običajno "
"informacije o tem, kaj aplikacija počne, na primer naslov spletne strani, ki "
"si jo ogledujete v spletnem brskalniku, ali ime datoteke dokumenta, odprtega "
"v urejevalniku besedil."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are located near the top of many applications, typically directly "
"underneath the <link linkend=\"visualdict-menubar\">menu bar</link>. They "
"provide access to many common functions of the running application, like "
"<emphasis>Save</emphasis> or <emphasis>Print</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Nahajajo se blizu vrha številnih aplikacij, običajno neposredno pod <link "
"linkend=\"visualdict-menubar\">menijsko vrstico</link>. Omogočajo dostop do "
"številnih običajnih funkcij delujočih aplikacij, kot je <emphasis>Shrani</"
"emphasis> ali <emphasis>Natisni</emphasis>."

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tree View"
msgstr "Drevesni pogled"

#. Tag: entry
#: ui.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A Tree View allows you to select from a hierarchical list of options. A "
"section, or category, of the Tree View may be unexpanded, in which case no "
"options will appear beneath it and the arrow to the left of the title will "
"be pointing right, toward the title. It may also be expanded, in which case "
"several options will be listed below it, and the arrow to the left of the "
"title will be pointing down, toward the options. To expand a portion of the "
"tree view, click the arrow to the left of the title of the section you wish "
"to expand, double-click on the title, or select the title using your "
"keyboard's arrow keys and press the &Enter; or <keycap>+</keycap> key. To "
"minimize a portion of the tree view, you may also click the arrow, double-"
"click on the title, or press the &Enter; or <keycap>-</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Drevesni pogled vam omogoča izbiro s hierarhičnega seznama možnosti. "
"Razdelek ali kategorija drevesnega pogleda je lahko nerazširjena, v tem "
"primeru se pod njim ne bodo prikazale nobene možnosti in puščica na levi "
"strani naslova bo kazala desno proti naslovu. Lahko se tudi razširi, v tem "
"primeru bo pod njim navedenih več možnosti, puščica na levi strani naslova "
"pa bo usmerjena navzdol proti možnostim. Če želite razširiti del drevesnega "
"pogleda, kliknite puščico levo od naslova odseka, ki ga želite razširiti, "
"dvokliknite naslov ali izberite naslov s puščičnimi tipkami na tipkovnici in "
"pritisnite &Enter; ali tipko <keycap>+</keycap>. Če želite pomanjšati del "
"drevesnega pogleda, lahko tudi kliknete puščico, dvokliknete naslov ali "
"pritisnete &Enter; ali tipko <keycap>-</keycap>."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common Menus"
msgstr "Skupni meniji"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many &kde; applications contain these menus. However, most applications will "
"have more menu entries than those listed here, and others may be missing "
"some of the entries listed here."
msgstr ""
"Veliko &kde; aplikacij vsebuje te menije, vendar bo večina aplikacij imela "
"več menijskih vnosov od tistih, ki so navedeni tukaj, drugim pa morda "
"manjkajo nekateri tukaj navedeni vnosi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: ui.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Menu Bar"
msgstr "Menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: phrase
#: ui.docbook:758
#, no-c-format
msgid "A menubar"
msgstr "Menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menubar in <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/graphics/"
"gwenview/\">&gwenview;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Menijska vrstica na <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/graphics/"
"gwenview/\">&gwenview;</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some applications, like &dolphin;, do not show a menubar by default. You can "
"show it by pressing <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>. You can "
"also use this to hide the menubar in applications that support doing so."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere aplikacije, kot je &dolphin;, privzeto ne prikažejo menijske "
"vrstice. Lahko jo prikažete s pritiskom <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></"
"keycombo>. To lahko uporabite tudi za skrivanje menijske vrstice v "
"aplikacijah, ki to podpirajo."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu allows you to perform operations on the "
"currently open file and access common tasks in applications."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> omogoča izvajanje operacij s trenutno "
"odprto datoteko in dostop do običajnih opravil v aplikacijah."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common menu items include:"
msgstr "Ta meni običajno vsebuje naslednje elemente:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a new file."
msgstr "Ustvari novo datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Window</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo okno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:792
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a new window."
msgstr "Odpre novo okno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpri ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:802
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens an already existing file."
msgstr "Odpre že obstoječo datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the file. If the file already exists it will be overwritten."
msgstr "Shrani datoteko. Če datoteka že obstaja, bo prepisana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the file with a new filename."
msgstr "Shrani datoteko z novim imenom datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:831
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves all open files."
msgstr "Shrani vse odprte datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Znova naloži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:841
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reloads the current file."
msgstr "Ponovno naloži trenutno datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reload All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponovno naloži vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reloads all open files."
msgstr "Ponovno naloži vse odprte datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Natisni...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prints the file. Use <guilabel>Print to File (PDF)</guilabel> to generate a "
"&PDF; file or select a range of pages to print only these pages to a new "
"&PDF; file"
msgstr ""
"Natisne datoteko. Uporabite <guilabel>Natisni v datoteko (PDF)</guilabel> za "
"ustvarjanje &PDF; datoteko ali izberite obseg strani, da natisnete samo te "
"strani v nov &PDF; mapa"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:871
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes the current file."
msgstr "Zapre trenutno datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:877
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapri vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes all open files."
msgstr "Zapre vse odprte datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:890
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exits the program."
msgstr "Izhod iz programa."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:899
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Urejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu allows you to modify the currently open "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> omogoča spreminjanje trenutno odprte datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:910
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo the last action you performed in the file."
msgstr "Razveljavi zadnje dejanje, ki ste ga izvedli v datoteki."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponovi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid "Redo the last action you performed in the file."
msgstr "Ponovite zadnje dejanje, ki ste ga izvedli v datoteki."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:926
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the currently selected portion of the file, if any, and places a "
"copy of it in the clipboard buffer."
msgstr ""
"Odstrani trenutno izbrani del datoteke, če obstaja, in postavi njegovo "
"kopijo v medpomnilnik odložišča."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Places a copy of the currently selected portion of the file, if any, in the "
"clipboard buffer."
msgstr ""
"Postavi kopijo trenutno izbranega dela datoteke, če obstaja, v medpomnilnik "
"odložišča."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies the first item in the clipboard buffer to the current location in the "
"file, if any."
msgstr ""
"Kopira prvi element v medpomnilniku odložišča na trenutno lokacijo v "
"datoteki, če obstaja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izberi vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects the entire contents of the currently open file."
msgstr "Izbere celotno vsebino trenutno odprte datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:969
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to search for text in the currently open file."
msgstr "Omogoča vam iskanje besedila v trenutno odprti datoteki."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Replace...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zamenjaj ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:983
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to search for text in the currently open file and replace it with "
"something else."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča iskanje besedila v trenutno odprti datoteki in njegovo zamenjavo z "
"nečim drugim."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:990
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F3</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F3</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:994
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next match of the last Find operation."
msgstr "Pojdi na naslednje ujemanje zadnje operacije Najdi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Poišči prejšnje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous match of the last Find operation."
msgstr "Pojdi na prejšnje ujemanje zadnje operacije Najdi."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:1013
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1014
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu allows you to change the layout of the "
"currently open file and/or the running application."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> omogoča spreminjanje postavitve trenutno "
"odprte datoteke in/ali delujoče aplikacije."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu has different options depending on the application you are using."
msgstr ""
"Ta meni ima različne možnosti, odvisno od aplikacije, ki jo uporabljate."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu"
msgstr "Meni Orodja"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu allows you to perform certain actions on "
"the currently open file."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> omogoča izvajanje določenih dejanj na "
"trenutno odprti datoteki."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1029
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Automatic Spell "
"Checking</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Samodejno "
"preverjanje črkovanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check for spelling errors as you type. For more information, see <xref "
"linkend=\"spellcheck-auto\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Med tipkanjem preverite črkovalne napake. Za več informacij glejte <xref "
"linkend=\"spellcheck-auto\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spelling...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Črkovanje ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This initiates the spellchecking program - a program designed to help the "
"user catch and correct any spelling errors. For more information, see <xref "
"linkend=\"spellcheck-check\"/>."
msgstr ""
"To sproži program za preverjanje črkovanja - program, ki je zasnovan tako, "
"da uporabniku pomaga odkriti in popraviti morebitne črkovalne napake. Za več "
"informacij glejte <xref linkend=\"spellcheck-check\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spelling (from cursor)...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Črkovanje (od kazalca)...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1054
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This initiates the spellchecking program, but only checks the portion of the "
"document from the current location of the cursor to the end. For more "
"information, see <xref linkend=\"spellcheck-check\"/>."
msgstr ""
"To zažene program za preverjanje črkovanja, vendar preveri le del dokumenta "
"od trenutne lokacije kazalca do konca. Za več informacij glejte <xref "
"linkend=\"spellcheck-check\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spellcheck Selection...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbira preverjanja črkovanja ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This initiates the spellchecking program, but only checks the currently "
"selected text in the document. For more information, see <xref linkend="
"\"spellcheck-check\"/>."
msgstr ""
"To zažene program za preverjanje črkovanja, vendar preveri samo trenutno "
"izbrano besedilo v dokumentu. Za več informacij glejte <xref linkend="
"\"spellcheck-check\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1072
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Change Dictionary...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spremeni slovar ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1075
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to change the dictionary used to check spellings. For more "
"information, see <xref linkend=\"spellcheck-config\"/>."
msgstr ""
"To vam omogoča, da spremenite slovar, ki se uporablja za preverjanje "
"črkovanja. Za več informacij glejte <xref linkend=\"spellcheck-config\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> allows you to customize the application."
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> vam omogočajo prilagajanje aplikacije."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1089
#, no-c-format
msgid "This menu typically contains the following items:"
msgstr "Ta meni običajno vsebuje naslednje elemente:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1093
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Menubar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži menijsko "
"vrstico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle the Menubar display</action> on and off. Once hidden it can "
"be made visible using the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo> again. If the menubar is hidden, the context "
"menu opened with a right mouse button click anywhere in the view area has an "
"extra entry <guimenuitem>Show Menubar</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Vklop in izklop prikaza menijske vrstice</action>. Ko je skrita, jo "
"lahko znova naredite vidno z bližnjico <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>. Če je menijska vrstica skrita, ima kontekstni "
"meni, ki se odpre z desnim klikom miške kjerkoli v območju pogleda, dodaten "
"vnos <guimenuitem>Pokaži menijsko vrstico</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1110
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži vrstico stanja</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of the statusbar on and off. Some &kde; applications use "
"statusbar at the bottom of their screen to display useful information."
msgstr ""
"Vklopi in izklopi prikaz vrstice stanja. Nekatere &kde; aplikacije "
"uporabljajo vrstico stanja na dnu zaslona za prikaz uporabnih informacij."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1122
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Toolbars Shown</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Prikazane orodne vrstice</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to show and hide the various toolbars supported by the "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča prikaz in skrivanje različnih orodnih vrstic, ki jih podpira "
"aplikacija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži vrstico stanja</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked, this displays a small bar at the bottom of the application "
"containing information about the status. When unchecked the status bar is "
"hidden."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označeno, prikaže majhno vrstico na dnu aplikacije, ki vsebuje "
"informacije o statusu. Ko ni potrjeno, je vrstica stanja skrita."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to enable, disable, and modify keyboard shortcuts. For more "
"information, see <xref linkend=\"shortcuts\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča omogočanje, onemogočanje in spreminjanje bližnjic na tipkovnici. Za "
"več informacij glejte <xref linkend=\"shortcuts\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj orodne vrstice ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to customize the contents, layout, text, and icons of toolbars. "
"For more information, see <xref linkend=\"toolbars\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča prilagajanje vsebine, postavitve, besedila in ikon orodnih vrstic. "
"Za več informacij si oglejte <xref linkend=\"toolbars\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Notifications...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj obvestila ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item displays a standard &kde; notifications configuration dialog, "
"where you can change the notifications (sounds, visible messages, &etc;) "
"used by the application."
msgstr ""
"Ta element prikaže standardni &kde; pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo "
"obvestil, kjer lahko spremenite obvestila (zvoke, vidna sporočila itd.), ki "
"jih uporablja aplikacija."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information how to configure notifications please read the "
"documentation for the &systemsettings; module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"kcmnotify/index.html\">Manage Notifications</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o konfiguraciji obvestil preberite dokumentacijo za "
"&systemsettings; modul <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kcmnotify/index.html"
"\">Upravljanje obvestil</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure <replaceable>Application</"
"replaceable>...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"<replaceable>Aplikacijo</replaceable>...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the configuration panel for the currently running application."
msgstr "Odpre konfiguracijsko ploščo za trenutno delujočo aplikacijo."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu gives you access to the application's "
"documentation and other useful resources."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> vam omogoča dostop do dokumentacije aplikacije "
"in drugih uporabnih virov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem><replaceable>Application</"
"replaceable> Handbook</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem><replaceable>Aplikacija</"
"replaceable> Priročnik</guimenuitem >"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Invokes the KDE Help system</action> starting at the running "
"application's handbook."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikliče sistem pomoči KDE</action> začenši s priročnikom za "
"trenutno delujočo aplikacijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>What's This?</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kaj je to?</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Changes the mouse cursor to a combination arrow and question mark.</"
"action> Clicking on items within the application; will open a help window "
"(if one exists for the particular item) explaining the item's function."
msgstr ""
"<action>Spremeni kazalec miške v kombinacijo puščice in vprašaja.</action> "
"Klik na elemente v aplikaciji; bo odprlo okno s pomočjo (če obstaja za "
"določen element) z razlago funkcije elementa."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1223
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tip of the Day</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nasvet dneva</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>opens the <guilabel>Tip of the Day</guilabel> dialog</"
"action>. You can page through all the tips by using the buttons on the "
"dialog and select to show the tips at startup."
msgstr ""
"This command <action>opens the <guilabel>Tip of the Day</guilabel> dialog</"
"action>. You can page through all the tips by using the buttons on the "
"dialog and select to show the tips at startup."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note: Not all applications provide these tips."
msgstr "Opomba: vse aplikacije ne nudijo teh nasvetov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1237
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Report Bug...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prijavi napako ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens the Bug report dialog</action> where you can report a bug or "
"request a <quote>wishlist</quote> feature."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre pogovorno okno za poročilo o napaki</action>, kjer lahko "
"prijavite napako ali zahtevate funkcijo <quote>seznama želja</quote>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Donate</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Donirajte</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/community/donations\">Donations "
"page</ulink> where you can support &kde; and its projects."
msgstr ""
"Odpre <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/community/donations\">stran z "
"donacijami</ulink>, kjer lahko podprete &kde; in njene projekte."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Switch Application Language...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preklop jezika aplikacije ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens a dialog</action> where you can edit the <guilabel>Primary "
"language</guilabel> and <guilabel>Fallback language</guilabel> for this "
"application."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre pogovorno okno</action>, kjer lahko uredite <guilabel>Primarni "
"jezik</guilabel> in <guilabel>Nadomestni jezik</guilabel> za to aplikacijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>About <replaceable>Application</"
"replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>O <replaceable>Aplikaciji</"
"replaceable></guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: ui.docbook:1273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display version and author information for the running application."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo informacije o različici in avtorju za delujočo aplikacijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: ui.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>About KDE</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>O KDE</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: ui.docbook:1282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This displays the &kde; Development Platform version and other basic "
"information."
msgstr ""
"To prikaže različico razvojne platforme &kde; in druge osnovne informacije."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thanks and Acknowledgments"
msgstr "Hvala in zahvala"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Special thanks to an anonymous Google Code-In 2011 participant for writing "
"much of this documentation."
msgstr ""
"Hvala anonimnemu udeležencu Google Code-In 2011 za pisanje večjega dela tega "
"razdelka."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:1307
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Pogoste bližnjice na tipkovnici"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &plasma-workspaces; provide keyboard shortcuts that allow you to perform "
"many tasks without touching your mouse. If you use your keyboard frequently, "
"using these can save you lots of time."
msgstr ""
"&plasma-workspaces; ponujajo bližnjice na tipkovnici, ki vam omogočajo "
"izvajanje številnih opravil, brez da bi se dotaknili miške. Če tipkovnico "
"uporabljate pogosto, lahko z uporabo teh prihranite veliko časa."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This list contains the most common shortcuts supported by the workspace "
"itself and many applications available within. Every application also "
"provides its own shortcuts, so be sure to check their manuals for a "
"comprehensive listing."
msgstr ""
"Ta seznam vsebuje najpogostejše bližnjice, ki jih podpira sam delovni "
"prostor ter številne aplikacije, ki so na voljo v njem. Vsaka aplikacija "
"ponuja tudi lastne bližnjice, zato preverite njihove priročnike za izčrpen "
"seznam."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <keysym>Meta</keysym> key described below is a generic name for the "
"custom key found on many different keyboards. On keyboards designed for "
"&Microsoft; &Windows;, this key is usually called the <keysym>Windows</"
"keysym> key, and will have a picture of the &Windows; logo. On keyboards "
"designed for &Mac; computers, this key is known as the <keysym>Command</"
"keysym> key and will have a picture of the <trademark class=\"registered"
"\">Apple</trademark> logo and/or the <keycap>⌘</keycap> symbol. On keyboards "
"designed for &UNIX; systems, this key is really known as the <keysym>Meta</"
"keysym> key and is typically labeled with a diamond: <keycap>◆</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj opisana tipka <keysym>Meta</keysym> je generično ime za tipko po "
"meri, ki jo najdete na številnih različnih tipkovnicah. Na tipkovnicah, "
"zasnovanih za &Microsoft; &Windows;, se ta tipka običajno imenuje tipka "
"<keysym>Windows</keysym> in bo imela sliko logotipa &Windows;. Na "
"tipkovnicah zasnovanih za &Mac; računalnike, je ta tipka znana kot tipka "
"<keysym>Command</keysym> in bo imela sliko logotipa <trademark class="
"\"registered\">Apple</trademark> in/ali <keycap>⌘</keycap > simbol. Na "
"tipkovnicah zasnovanih za sisteme &UNIX;, je ta ključ v resnici znan kot "
"ključ <keysym>Meta</keysym> in je običajno označen z diamantom: <keycap>◆</"
"keycap>."

