#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:1923
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Volume and Brightness"
msgstr "Spreminjanje glasnosti in svetlosti"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1925
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to the standard keys, many computer keyboards and laptops "
"nowadays have special keys or buttons to change the speaker volume, as well "
"as the brightness of your monitor if applicable. If present, you can use "
"these keys in the &plasma-workspaces; to perform those tasks."
msgstr ""
"Poleg standardnih tipk ima veliko današnjih računalniških tipkovnic in "
"prenosnih računalnikov posebne tipke ali gumbe za spreminjanje glasnosti "
"zvočnika in svetlosti vašega monitorja. Če so prisotni, jih lahko uporabite "
"v &plasma-workspaces; za opravljanje teh nalog."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not have such keys, see <xref linkend=\"kbd-modifying\"/> for "
"information on how to assign keys for these tasks."
msgstr ""
"Če nimate takih ključev, glejte <xref linkend=\"kbd-modifying\"/> za "
"informacije o tem, kako dodeliti ključe za te naloge."

